Fletcher Building Infrastructure Chief Quits to Head Meridian

-- B y   C h r i s   B o u r k e
-- 
2011-10-03T20:05:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/fletcher-building-infrastructure-chief-quits-to-head-meridian.html
Fletcher Building Ltd. (FBU)  said that Mark
Binns, chief executive officer of its infrastructure division,
resigned in a statement today. Binns has accepted the position
of chief executive officer of energy company Meridian Energy
Ltd, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Bourke at 
 cbourke4@bloomberg.net  